    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 10</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 28</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You touch a target and cause a seal to appear, causing the target to become paralyzed. The seal uses a seal slot, and can be dispelled by using this technique on the target and making a Fuinjutsu check (DC 10 + your HD when you performed the first seal).</p>\n\n\n\n",
